metadata.name: Time by the Pond:  5lbs
metadata.description:
The journey has just begun.  Usually, the first couple are easy.  It took me 11 days to reach my first milestone.  
Today, 10/21/22 I went to the duck pond by my house. 
The ducks and geese were playful. A man and his dog arrived, almost like it was their routine. They were beautifully lit along the bank, and I found myself in a perfect spot for a backlit image.  Luck has found me this day!
The sun is warm and fall is in full swing. It is the season of change.  I am changing. 
This is the first image of this collection. 
I will celebrate every 5 because it means I am progressing and moving forward to my goal.
On to the next image! See you at 10lbs!
